---
title: Smokey Pork Schnitzel & Beetroot Relish with Cheesy Lemon Crushed Potatoes & Apple Slaw
description: A classic schnitzel is always best served with a side of potatoes. We’re jazzing things up tonight by crushing the potatoes with a squeeze of lemon juice. Crumb the pork with the barbecue seasoning for a smokey flavour and serve with a sweet and vibrant beetroot relish to bring the flavours together and make them sing!
